doesnt-need-listen-through-your-microphone-serve-you-creepy-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20it's%20not%20true%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20want%20evidence%20of%20Meta%20and%20Zuckerberg's%20startling%20unpopularity%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20click%20away.%20A%20staggering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2025%2F02%2F19%2Fhow-americans-view-elon-musk-and-mark-zuckerberg%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-thirds%20of%20Americans%20have%20a%20negative%20view%20of%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20Pew%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20we're%20here%2C%20we%20may%20as%20well%20note%20that%20social%20media%20is%20really%20good%20at%20spreading%20false%20messages%20about%20things%20that%20seem%20true%2C%20or%20that%20people%20want%20to%20seem%20true.%20This%20isn't%20something%20we're%20supposed%20to%20spend%20time%20worrying%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-donald-trump-moderation-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20our%20new%20political%20climate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20been%20true%20and%20it%20remains%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%2C%20periodically%2C%20Meta's%20users%20rise%20up%20to%20pass%20along%20proclamations%20about%20Meta's%20plans%20to%20screw%20them%20over.%20Or%20to%20pass%20along%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-goodbye-meta-ai-train-generative-post-copypasta-profile-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproclamations%20they%20think%20will%20protect%20them%20from%20Meta%20screwing%20them%20over%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20all%20gibberish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20Meta%20rolled%20out%20a%20new%20feature%20that%20lets%20users%20share%20their%20location%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20or%20a%20subset%20of%20them%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20predict%20that%20users%20might%20fear%20the%20worst%20%E2%80%94%20