%3Cp%3EThrough%20these%2C%20we%20learn%20of%20Alex's%20aunt%20Gladys%20(Amy%20Madigan)%2C%20an%20elderly%20woman%20who%20wears%20a%20red%20wig%2C%20colorful%20clothes%2C%20and%20too%20much%20red%20lipstick.%20She%20comes%20to%20Alex's%20house%20with%20a%20small%20tree%20that%20looks%20like%20it%20has%20dead%20branches.%20It's%20revealed%20near%20the%20end%20of%20the%20movie%20that%20it's%20some%20kind%20of%20voodoo%20tree%3A%20when%20Gladys%20puts%20some%20of%20her%20blood%20on%20a%20branch%20and%20wraps%20somebody's%20belongings%20or%20hair%20around%20it%2C%20that%20person%20goes%20under%20her%20spell%20once%20she%20breaks%20the%20branch%20and%20rings%20a%20small%20bell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20putting%20Alex's%20parents%20under%20her%20spell%2C%20she%20tells%20Alex%20to%20send%20her%20the%20belongings%20of%20all%2017%20of%20his%20classmates.%20She%20is%20the%20one%20responsible%20for%20the%20kids'%20disappearance.%20Gladys%2C%20who%20tells%20Alex%20she's%20ill%2C%20believes%20the%20children%20will%20make%20her%20better.%20They%20have%20all%20been%20in%20Alex's%20basement%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustine%20and%20Archer%20come%20to%20Alex's%20house%20hoping%20to%20find%20answers.%20They%20are%20welcomed%20by%20Paul%2C%20who%20also%20stumbled%20upon%20what%20Gladys%20was%20doing%20from%20a%20tip%20from%20a%20drug%20addict.%20Both%20Paul%20and%20the%20addict%20are%20now%20under%20her%20spell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e2b9727-960c-4cb0-9095-a2e5f586df90%5C%22%3EThe%20bloody%20ending%20all%20goes%20down%20at%20Alex's%20house%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boy%20walking%20to%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689642caf748d8c055f72e32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStay%20clear%20of%20this%20house.%3Cp%3ENew%20Line%20Cinema%2FWarner%20Bros.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20Justine%20and%20Archer%20are%20in%