0medical%20records%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangione-unitedhealth-ceo-killing-person-what-to-know-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Mangione%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20Maryland%20native%20accused%20in%20the%20December%20shooting%20murder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrian-thompson-unitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20records%20included%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20diagnoses%20as%20well%20as%20specific%20medical%20complaints%20made%20by%20Mr.%20Mangione%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20lawyers%20complained%20in%20their%20own%20filing%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20prosecutors%20and%20the%20defense%20agree%20that%20Seidemann's%20May%2014%20subpoena%20asked%20Aetna%20for%20very%20limited%20data%2C%20just%20Mangione's%20health%20insurance%20account%20number%20and%20the%20period%20of%20time%20he%20was%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%20small%20patch%20of%20common%20ground%2C%20the%20sides%20diverge%20widely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%2C%20led%20by%20attorney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-healthcare-uhc-ceo-shooting-suspect-arrested-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKaren%20Friedman%20Agnifilo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wrote%20last%20month%20that%20Seidemann%20should%20never%20have%20asked%20directly%20for%20Mangione's%20health%20insurance%20account%20number%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20protected%20under%20HIPAA%2C%20the%20federal%20Health%20Insurance%20Portability%20and%20Accountability%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20requested%20information%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20protected%20by%20HIPAA%2C%20since%20it%20did%20not%20relate%20to%20a%20condition%2C%20treatment%2C%20or%20payment%20for%20health%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Seidemann%20countered%20in%20Friday's%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sides%20also%20differ%20on%20what%20happened%20once%20Aetna%20attached%20Mangione's%20entire%20healthcare%20history%2C%20in%20four%20files%2C%20to%20its%20June%2012%2C%20supboeana-response%20email%20to%20Seidemann.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeidemann%20wrote%20in%20Friday's%20filing%20that%20his%20subpoena%20%26quot%3Bwas%20lawful%20and%20properly%20drafted%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%2C%20as%20required%2C%20it%20directed%20Aetna%20to%20return%20the%20requested%20materials%20to%20the%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20accuses%20Seidemann%20of%20sitting%20on%20the%20sensitive%20records%20for%2012%20days%20before%20forwarding%20them%20to%20the%20judge.%20They%20additionally%20want%20to%20know%20how%20Aetna%20wound%20up%20sending%20the%20records%20directly%20to%20the%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20asked%20the%20judge%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluigi-mangiones-judge-new-york-murder-gregory-carro-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Gregory%20Carro%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20order%20%26quot%3Ba%20full%20evidentiary%20hearing%26quot%3B%20to%20determine%20possible%20penalties%2C%20including%20kicking%20Seidemann%20off%20the%20case.%20They've%20asked%20that%20the%20hearing%20include%20sworn%20testimony%20and%20the%20surrender%20of%20correspondence%20between%20prosecutors%20and%20Aetna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20the%20judge%20had%20not%20issued%20a%20decision%20on%20calling%20such%20a%20hearing.%20A%20defense%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Friday's%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20state%20case%2C%20Mangione%20is%20charged%20with%20murder%20in%20a%20federal%20indictment%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-jury-voted-against-death-penalty-terrorist-luigi-mangione-harder-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseeks%20the%20death%20penalty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20another%2C%20more%20behind-the-scenes%20battle%2C%20prosecutors%20in%20both%2