illimeters%20and%20a%20weight%20of%20somewhere%20between%207.7%20and%208.2%20ounces%2C%20it's%20widely%20considered%20a%20midweight%2C%20standard-thickness%20paddle.%20The%20paddle's%20balanced%20nature%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20some%20standout%20features%2C%20like%20its%20surface%2C%20which%20is%20made%20of%20a%20patent-pending%20blend%20of%20carbon%20fiber%20and%20Kevlar.%20Together%2C%20these%20materials%20make%20a%20surface%20that%20is%20stiff%2C%20durable%2C%20textured%2C%20and%20generates%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20paddle%20is%20also%20thermoformed%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20which%20is%20the%20gold-standard%20method%20used%20to%20mold%20and%20make%20the%20best%20pickleball%20paddles.%20This%20process%20involves%20heating%20and%20molding%20the%20materials%20under%20pressure%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20stiffer%20and%20more%20consistent%20paddle%20face.%20Practically%20speaking%2C%20thermoformed%20paddles%20have%20enhanced%20sweet%20spots%20and%20are%20more%20durable.%20Another%20feature%20you%20can't%20see%20but%20can%20feel%20is%20the%20FlexFoam%20perimeter%2C%20which%20dampens%20vibration%20and%20makes%20even%20a%20smash%20feel%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20court%2C%20this%20was%20my%20favorite%20paddle%20of%20the%20bunch.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I'd%20consider%20myself%20a%20solid%20middle-of-the-road%20player%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20the%20way%20this%20paddle%20felt%20and%20played.%20It%20was%20heavy%20enough%20that%20I%20felt%20stable%20and%20was%20consistently%20hitting%20well%2C%20but%20not%20so%20heavy%20that%20I%20was%20working%20overtime%20to%20get%20the%20ball%20over%20the%20net.%20The%20paddle%20supported%20my%20natural%20swing%20and%20allowed%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20technique%20to%20better%20understand%20my%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20on%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20paddle%20that%20grows%20with%20you%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20sophisticated%20enough%20that%20it'll%20support%20an%20advanced%20play%20style%2C%20but%20forgiving%20enough%20to%20give%20novices%20confidence.%20If%20you%20come%20to%20learn%20you're%20all%20about%20power%20or%20finesse%2C%20you%20can%20graduate%20to%20something%20more%20specialized%2C%20but%20for%20beginners%20or%20versatile%20players%20who%20want%20a%20paddle%20that%20does%20everything%20well%2C%20this%20is%20it.%20And%20at%20a%20great%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221903ed59-4c99-4fe6-bdd4-2aaa9344c80b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20a%20very%20accessible%20paddle.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPart%20of%20what%20makes%20pickleball%20so%20appealing%20to%20so%20many%20is%20the%20low%20barrier%20to%20entry%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20smaller%20learning%20curve%20compared%20to%20most%20racquet%20sports.%20And%20the%20plethora%20of%20affordable%2C%20quality%20paddles%20out%20there%20makes%20the%20sport%20all%20the%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20get%20two%20paddles%20for%20the%20price%20of%20one%2C%20plus%20extras%20to%20get%20you%20started.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20%2440%2C%20the%20JoncAye%20Blitz%20set%20comes%20with%20two%20USAPA-approved%20pickleball%20paddles%2C%20four%20balls%2C%20and%20a%20drawstring%20bag%20for%20traveling.%20Most%20%26quot%3Bbudget%26quot%3B%20paddles%20of%20the%20same%20quality%20run%20for%20%2450%20to%20%24100%20for%20just%20one%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%208.125%20inches%2C%20this%20is%20a%20wide%20paddle%20with%20a%20huge%20sweet%20spot.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%2C%20plus%20the%20smooth%20fiberglass%20surface%20(which%20doesn't%20offer%20much%20spin%20potential)%2C%20makes%20these%20paddles%20more%20forgiving%20for%20beginners.%20The%20JoncAye%20Blitz%20paddles%20were%20the%20first%20paddles%20I%20ever%20bought%2C%20and%20they've%20held%20up%20surprisingly%20well%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years.%20Other%20than%20some%20scratches%20on%20the%20surface%20and%20some%20grip%20wear%20and%20tear%20(which%20can%20be%20easily%20fixed%20with%20new%20grip%20tape)%2C%20the%20paddles%20function%20just%20as%20they%20did%20when%20I%20bought%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20paddle%20like%20this%20doesn't%20offer%20many%20advanced%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20but%20it%20does%20offer%20a%20solid%20set%20at%20an%20unbeatable%20value.%20Plus%2C%20with%20two%20paddles%2C%20you'll%20always%20have%20gear%20for%20a%20buddy%20to%20play%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f603943-09a0-46f6-9b22-43d63260279b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20beginners%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20beginners%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20the%20name%20says%20%26quot%3Bpower%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SLK%20EVO%20Power%20XL%20is%20really%20a%20hybrid.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EControl%20and%20power%20may%20be%20completely%20different%20play%20styles%2C%20but%20beginners%20need%20to%20develop%20these%20skills%20simultaneously%20%E2%80%94%20an%20understanding%20of%20how%20to%20generate%20speed%20and%20strength%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20to%20control%20where%20the%20ball%20ends%20up.%20Don't%20be%20intimidated%20by%20the%20name%2C%20the%20SLK%20EVO%20Power%20XL%20is%20the%20best%20pickleball%20paddle%20for%20beginners%20because%20it%20gives%20you%20the%20boost%20you%20need%20to%20build%20confidence%20on%20the%20court%20at%20a%20beginner-friendly%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20brand%20calls%20it%20a%20paddle%20for%20%26quot%3Badvancing%20players%20who%20crave%20power%20without%20sacrificing%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20a%20scale%20of%201-10%2C%20the%20brand%20rates%20this%20a%205.5%20for%20power%20and%207.5%20for%20control%2C%20suggesting%20this%20paddle%20actually%20is%20a%20bit%20better%20for%20control%20after%20all.%20That%20balanced%20feel%2C%20not%20leaning%20in%20too%20heavily%20to%20any%20play%20style%2C%20is%20great%20for%20those%20still%20getting%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20paddle%20is%20lightweight%2C%20but%20has%20more%20pop%20than%20others%20in%20the%20same%20weight%20class.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThanks%20to%20more%20advanced%20features%20like%20the%20CarbonFusion%20carbon%20fiber%20surface%2C%20polymer%20core%2C%20and%20thermoformed%20construction%2C%20this%20paddle%20will%20be%20forgiving%20when%20you%20start%20playing%20but%20can%20grow%20with%20you%20as%20you%20learn%20how%20to%20put%20some%20spin%20on%20your%20returns%2C%20dink%20ever%20so%20softly%2C%20and%20lob%20with%20serious%20power.%20At%20%24100%2C%20it's%20on%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20price%20tier%20but%20still%20feels%20like%20an%20investment%20to%20keep%20you%20committed%20to%20getting%20out%20and%20playing%20a%20few%20times%20each%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a78ca1d0-f751-4703-877d-96862c17361e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20advanced%20players%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20advanced%20players%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20all%20of%20the%20most%20experienced%20pickleballers%20in%20the%20testing%20group%20agreed%20on%20one%20thing%3A%20the%20Wilson%20Vesper%20is%20the%20best%20paddle%20for%20advanced%20players.%20There%20are%20two%20models%20to%20choose%20from%3A%20the%20Wilson%20Vesper%20Power%20and%20the%20Wilson%20Vesper%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20you're%20an%20advanced%20player%2C%20gear%20really%20matters.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20you%20already%20have%20solid%20technique%2C%20the%20right%20equipment%20can%20help%20you%20make%20marginal%20gains%20that%20build%20on%20your%20already%20existing%20skills%20and%20improve%20performance.%20The%20Vesper%20Power%20and%20Vesper%20Control%20are%20very%20similar%2C%20but%20each%20paddle%20features%20slightly%20different%20details%20to%20amplify%20your%20power%20or%20control%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%2017%20millimeters%2C%20the%20Wilson%20Vesper%20Control%20is%20the%20thickest%20option%20on%20this%20list.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat%20thickness%2C%20paired%20with%20the%20gritty%20raw%20carbon%20fiber%20face%2C%20dampens%20the%20power%20from%20your%20opponents'%20shots%20and%20helps%20you%20respond%20with%20delicate%20precision.%20The%20widebody%20shape%20makes%20for%20a%20larger%20sweet%20spot%2C%20but%20at%2016%20inches%20long%2C%20including%20a%205-inch-long%20handle%2C%20this%20paddle%20feels%20smaller%20than%20others%20on%20this%20list.%20One%20advanced%20tester%20said%20that%20while%20she%20felt%20really%20in%20control%20of%20the%20ball%20while%20using%20this%20paddle%2C%20getting%20used%20to%20the%20size%20was%20an%20adjustment.%20Because%20this%20paddle%20leans%20wider%20than%20longer%2C%20it%20lacks%20reach%2C%20which%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20wide%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222792%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20shot%20of%20a%20pickleball%20rally%20in%20action%20shows%20a%20player's%20arm%20extended%20with%20a%20Wilson%20paddle%20just%20after%20hitting%20a%20bright%20yellow%20pickleball.%20The%20ball%20is%20caught%20midair%2C%20hovering%20above%20the%20net%20on%20a%20blue%20court%20with%20multiple%20pickleball%20courts%20visible%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689642f0194a2d49b8ae47fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222094%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhether%20you%20play%20power%20or%20control%2C%20Wilson's%20Vesper%20line%20was%20our%20testers'%20top%20pick%20for%20advanced%20players.%3Cp%3ERemi%20Rosmarin%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Wilson%20Vesper%20Power%20is%20an%20elongated%20paddle%2C%20which%20gives%20it%20a%20smaller%20sweet%20spot.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20extended%20handle%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20for%20further%20shots%2C%20and%20with%20room%20for%20both%20hands%20on%20the%20handle%2C%20you%20can%20put%20your%20whole%20body%20behind%20the%20shot%20and%20really%20unleash%20your%20power.%20The%20FreeFlex%20open%20throat%20design%2C%20like%20a%20tennis%20racquet%2C%20helps%20increase%20swing%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20brand%20calls%20both%20of%20these%20paddles%20%26quot%3Bbarely%20legal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20bad%20thing%20at%20first%2C%20but%20it's%20actually%20a%20great%20way%20to%20market%20these%20paddles.%20In%20order%20to%20be%20approved%20for%20tournament%20use%2C%20a%20pickleball%20paddle%20has%20to%20meet%20USAPA%20standards%2C%20which%20are%20designed%20to%20ensure%20paddles%20are%20safe%20for%20use%20and%20don't%20give%20players%20an%20unfair%20advantage%20on%20the%20court.%20Wilson's%20claim%20that%20the%20Vesper%20paddles%20are%20barely%20legal%20really%20just%20means%20that%20these%20paddles%20are%20as%20advanced%20as%20possible%2C%20pushing%20the%20limit%20on%20what%20a%20paddle%20can%20be%20while%20still%20adhering%20to%20USAPA%20standards.%20At%20%24249%20each%2C%20these%20are%20the%20most%20expensive%20paddles%20on%20the%20list.%20But%2C%20if%20you're%20ready%20to%20uplevel%2C%20they%20really%20do%20deliver%20a%20premium%20experience%2C%20and%20then%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22192347b0-a2b5-42f3-8bc5-3b40d6e74a38%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20pickleball%20paddle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20neatly%20arranged%20grid%20of%20ten%20pickleball%20paddles%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20wooden%20deck%2C%20showcasing%20a%20range%20of%20brands%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20styles.%20The%20top%20row%20includes%20models%20from%20Wilson%2C%20JOOLA%2C%20Selkirk%2C%20SLK%2C%20and%20Paddletek%2C%20while%20the%20bottom%20row%20features%20Selkirk%2C%20Diadem%2C%20SLK%2C%20Nettie%2C%20and%20another%20Wilson%20paddle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6896405b194a2d49b8ae4780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPickleball%20paddles%20have%20subtle%20but%20significant%20differences.%20Here's%20what%20to%20look%20for%20depending%20on%20your%20play%20style.%20%3Cp%3ERemi%20Rosmarin%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20me%20understand%20the%20basics%20of%20paddle%20construction%20and%20how%20small%20details%20can%20affect%20your%20performance%20on%20the%20court%2C%20I%20consulted%20Jack%20Waite%2C%20director%20of%20racquet%20sports%20at%20Burning%20Tree%20Country%20Club%20and%20Professional%20Pickleball%20Registry%20coach%20developer%2C%20for%20some%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223469f779-5be6-4ab3-8601-a77b76e663a1%5C%22%3EWeight%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPaddles%20come%20in%20a%20range%20of%20weights%2C%20with%20most%20in%20the%20midweight%20range%20between%207.9%20and%208.2%20ounces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMidweight%20paddles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20the%20most%20balanced%20option%2C%20offering%20a%20blend%20of%20control%2C%20maneuverability%2C%20and%20power.%20Most%20players%20will%20do%20well%20with%20a%20midweight%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELightweight%20paddles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(7.8%20ounces%20or%20less)%20are%20easy%20to%20maneuver%20and%20swing.%20If%20you're%20a%20net%20player%20who%20reacts%20quickly%20to%20get%20volleys%20and%20blocks%2C%20a%20lightweight%20paddle%20is%20a%20good%20option%20that%20can%20enhance%20your%20play%20style.%20Lightweight%20paddles%20are%20also%20great%20for%20beginners%20who%20need%20accuracy%20and%20control%2C%20and%20those%20with%20a%20history%20of%20arm%20injury.%20For%20some%20players%2C%20particularly%20bigger%20and%20stronger%20folks%2C%20lightweight%20paddles%20may%20feel%20a%20bit%20flimsy%20%E2%80%94%20you%20might%20find%20yourself%20overexerting%20your%20energy%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeavyweight%20paddles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(8.3%20ounces%20and%20up)%20are%20often%20the%20choice%20for%20power%20players.%20Because%20they%20are%20heavier%2C%20these%20paddles%20generate%20more%20power%20with%20less%20effort.%20The%20added%20weight%20also%20often%20feels%20more%20stable%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20too%20heavy%20for%20you%2C%20it%20can%20slow%20your%20reaction%20time.%20If%20you're%20still%20learning%20proper%20pickleball%20technique%2C%20this%20probably%20isn't%20the%20right%20paddle%20weight.%20The%20exception%20is%20those%20who%20are%20naturally%20very%20strong%2C%20as%20this%20paddle%20weight%20might%20feel%20natural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c6be8e2-bca3-4ffa-88ed-e080346ef76f%5C%22%3ESurface%20material%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESurface%20material%20is%20about%20way%20more%20than%20aesthetics%3B%20it%20has%20a%20serious%20impact%20on%20the%20way%20the%20ball%20interacts%20with%20your%20paddle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFiberglass%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20materials%20on%20the%20market.%20It's%20economical%20and%20has%20a%20smooth%20texture%20that%20creates%20less%20friction%20when%20the%20ball%20meets%20the%20paddle%2C%20enhancing%20both%20pop%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECarbon%20fiber%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20more%20premium%20material%3B%20it's%20essentially%20thousands%20of%20carbon%20fibers%20woven%20together%20like%20a%20piece%20of%20fabric.%20The%20weave%20is%20lightweight%20but%20very%20strong%20and%20naturally%20textured%20for%20exceptional%20spin%2C%20friction%2C%20and%20superior%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20paddles%2C%20like%20the%20SLK%20HALO%20Pro%20XL%2C%20use%20%3Cstrong%3Ehybrid%20surfaces%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20that%20blend%20carbon%20fiber%20with%20durable%20Kevlar%20(a%20fiber%20that%20is%20five%20times%20stronger%20than%20steel)%20to%20enhance%20finesse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261085671-45dc-428b-8b8f-4c576b15b26c%5C%22%3ECore%20composition%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESandwiched%20between%20the%20paddle%20faces%20sits%20the%20core%20%E2%80%94%20the%20innermost%20section%20of%20the%20pickleball%20paddle%20and%20arguably%20one%20of%20its%20most%20crucial%20components.%20While%20you%20can't%20see%20it%2C%20the%20core%20composition%20greatly%20impacts%20the%20way%20a%20paddle%20performs%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20power%2C%20control%2C%20and%20durability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymer%2Fpolypropylene%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20commonly%20used%20materials%20for%20paddle%20cores%20%E2%80%94%20every%20one%20of%20our%20picks%20features%20a%20poly%20core.%20The%20balance%20of%20power%20and%20control%2C%20shock%20prevention%2C%20and%20quieter%20sound%20all%20contribute%20to%20the%20material's%20widespread%20use.%20Nomex%20is%20another%20frequently%20used%20core%20material.%20Its%20stiff%20and%20rigid%20construction%20makes%20it%20a%20powerhouse%20in%20delivering%20maximum%20power%20shots.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20extremely%20durable%20and%20resistant%20to%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22acb19ad7-377f-45d2-9baf-3fc7b037288a%5C%22%3EGrip%20size%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20grip%20size%3A%20circumference%20and%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECircumference%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20differences%20between%20grip%20circumferences%20are%20minuscule%20but%20really%20do%20matter.%20Waite%20said%20the%20standard%20grip%20size%20is%204.25%20inches%2C%20while%204%20inches%20is%20considered%20thin%20and%204.5%20inches%20is%20considered%20thick.%20Smaller%20grips%20allow%20for%20quicker%20paddle%20maneuverability.%20You%20can%20always%20make%20a%20grip%20thicker%20with%20overgrips%20for%20added%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELong%20handles%20(often%20denoted%20as%20%26quot%3BXL%26quot%3B)%20are%20great%20for%20players%20who%20want%20extra%20reach%20or%20prefer%20two-handed%20backhands.%20Short%20handles%20(often%20called%20%26quot%3BMax%26quot%3B%20paddles)%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20tend%20to%20maximize%20paddle%20face%20area%2C%20which%20means%20a%20larger%20sweet%20spot%20and%20a%20more%20forgiving%20paddle.%20%26quot%3BThe%20longer%20the%20grip%2C%20the%20smaller%20your%20paddle%20face%20area%2C%20so%20keep%20that%20in%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Waite%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adc20664-d24f-42f9-bd8c-8098cc8d290e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20pickleball%20paddles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20neatly%20arranged%20grid%20of%20ten%20pickleball%20paddles%20is%20displayed%20on%20a%20wooden%20deck%2C%20showcasing%20a%20range%20of%20brands%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20styles.%20The%20top%20row%20includes%20models%20from%20Wilson%2C%20JOOLA%2C%20Selkirk%2C%20SLK%2C%20and%20Paddletek%2C%20while%20the%20bottom%20row%20features%20Selkirk%2C%20Diadem%2C%20SLK%2C%20Nettie%2C%20and%20another%20Wilson%20paddle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689641d4cfc04e97619b20a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tested%20the%20pickleball%20paddles%20on%20the%20court%20with%20a%20range%20of%20players%20of%20varying%20skill%20levels%20and%20play%20styles.%3Cp%3ERemi%20Rosmarin%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20four%20months%2C%20I%20took%2012%20paddles%20out%20weekly%20and%20tested%20them%20on%20private%20courts%20with%20players%20at%20a%20variety%20of%20skill%20and%20experience%20levels.%20I'm%20certainly%20not%20an%20expert%20player.%20I%20tend%20to%20feel%20most%20at%20home%20playing%20at%20the%20baseline%2C%20hitting%20groundstrokes.%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20include%20testers%20who%20excel%20at%20gnarly%20power%20shots%20and%20precision%20placement%2C%20so%20we%20could%20fairly%20assess%20how%20different%20paddles%20fared%20for%20different%20play%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaddles%20were%20tested%20for%20full%20games%20and%20rotated%20between%20players%20before%20new%20games.%20These%20were%20usually%20doubles%2C%20so%20we%20were%20often%20able%20to%20test%20four%20paddles%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20aggregated%20verbal%20and%20written%20feedback%20from%20players%20after%20every%20pickleball%20session%2C%20considering%20their%20skill%20level%20and%20play%20style.%20Testing%20sessions%20could%20run%20anywhere%20from%2030%20minutes%20to%20two%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20factors%20like%20weather%20and%20endurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220463b83-1bf4-41a1-8f9d-c49edc9fbea8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EPickleball%20paddle%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20expensive%20paddles%20worth%20it%20for%20beginners%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20to%20buy%20an%20expensive%20paddle%20depends%20on%20more%20than%20just%20your%20skill%20level%2C%20but%20also%20your%20play%20frequency%20and%20goals.%20If%20you're%20a%20beginner%20and%20play%20infrequently%2C%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20splurge%20on%20an%20expensive%20paddle.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20play%20regularly%20but%20are%20not%20yet%20a%20highly%20skilled%20player%2C%20Waite%20suggests%20going%20for%20a%20paddle%20in%20the%20%24150%20to%20%24200%20range.%20%26quot%3BThe%20materials%20tend%20to%20be%20higher%20quality%2C%20and%20in%20this%20range%20you%20can%20find%20lots%20of%20paddles%20with%20bigger%20sweet%20spots%2C%20power%2C%20and%20control%20than%20the%20lower%20price%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsweet%20spot%26quot%3B%20and%20why%20does%20it%20matter%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20sweet%20spot%20on%20a%20pickleball%20paddle%20is%20located%20near%20the%20center.%20It's%20essentially%20the%20zone%20where%20your%20paddle%20and%20ball%20find%20perfect%20harmony%20on%20contact.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20hit%20it%2C%20you%20will%20feel%20like%20you%20have%20a%20combination%20of%20power%20and%20control%20with%20less%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20Waite%20said.%20When%20the%20ball%20hits%20outside%20the%20sweet%20spot%2C%20you%20might%20feel%20an%20uncomfortable%20vibration%20through%20the%20paddle%20or%20even%20feel%20like%20the%20ball%20is%20dead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELarger%20sweet%20spots%20are%20more%20forgiving%2C%20making%20them%20a%20good%20choice%20for%20beginners%20looking%20to%20elevate%20their%20game.%20But%20even%20with%20a%20larger%20sweet%20spot%2C%20improving%20shot%20consistency%20is%20a%20big%20feat.%20As%20Waite%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bconsistently%20hitting%20the%20sweet%20spot%20is%20something%20that%20separates%20the%20pros%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pickleball-paddles%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754681190000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68963faf194a2d49b8ae4765%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pickleball-paddles%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gear%20can%20make%20or%20break%20your%20pickleball%20experience.%20Our%20tester%20hit%20the%20courts%20weekly%20for%204%20months%20to%20find%20the%20best%20pickleball%20paddles%20for%20every%20type%20of%20player.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrosmarin%40businessinsider.com%20(Remi%20Rosmarin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pickleball-paddles%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20backpacked%20across%20Europe%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%2010%20things%20surprised%20me%20about%20the%202-week%20adventure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20stands%20with%20a%20backpack%20on%20in%20front%20of%20a%20train%20in%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63c181b402cb82001937