xplained%20clearly%2C%20with%20relevant%20new%20concepts%2C%20pros%20and%20cons%2C%20and%20exploratory%20thinking.%20It%20doesn't%20give%20you%20a%20final%20product%3B%20it%20helps%20you%20create%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ%3A%20Is%20Study%20Mode%20better%20for%20student%20learning%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefinitely.%20It%20explains%20concepts%20deeply%20and%20visually.%20Some%20charts%20reminded%20me%20of%20my%20old%20IB%20economics%20textbook.%20It%20balances%20ideal%20advice%20(like%20saving%2020%25%20of%20income)%20with%20realistic%20data%20(most%20Americans%20save%208%25%20or%20less).%20It%20also%20has%20features%20like%20quizzes%20I%20haven't%20tried%20yet%2C%20which%20could%20be%20great%20for%20learning%20Spanish%20or%20exam%20prep.%20But%20it's%20no%20substitute%20for%20a%20human%20teacher's%20emotional%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EQ%3A%20Any%20tips%20for%20Tech%20Memo%20readers%20using%20Study%20Mode%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20open-ended.%20Don't%20just%20ask%20for%20facts%20%E2%80%94%20ask%20why%20something%20works%2C%20what%20alternatives%20exist%2C%20or%20how%20designs%20function.%20Like%20a%20good%20classroom%2C%20it's%20about%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b5d9e46-2a56-44dd-a1f6-0d7e7cce77ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUser%20feedback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20hearing%20from%20readers.%20What%20do%20you%20want%20to%20see%20more%20of%2C%20or%20less%20of%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20though%3A%20This%20week%2C%20I%20want%20to%20hear%20back%20about%20how%20work%20has%20interrupted%20your%20summer%20chillin'%20plans.%20The%20most%20gruesome%20stories%20%3D%20the%20best.%20Let%20me%20know%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F