nsider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20life%20on%20the%20island%20has%20been%20wonderful.%20The%20Krehers%20have%20become%20more%20active%20as%20a%20family%20thanks%20to%20Puerto%20Rico's%20temperate%20climate%20and%20scores%20of%20scenic%20beaches%20and%20trails%2C%20and%20they've%20quickly%20built%20a%20support%20system%20in%20their%20kind%20and%20welcoming%20community.%20Maybe%20their%20kids%20will%20even%20end%20up%20being%20bilingual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20things%20are%20different%2C%20but%20you're%20not%20left%20wanting%2C%20like%20maybe%20some%20folks%20would%20imagine%2C%26quot%3B%20Kreher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20of%20four%20posing%20for%20a%20picture%20in%20front%20of%20a%20sign%20in%20Spanish.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893c8e4194a2d49b8ae2081%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222149%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharity%20and%20Ian%20Kreher%20with%20their%20two%20children.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Charity%20Kreher%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20white%20sand%20beaches%2C%20lively%20culture%2C%20and%20relatively%20fast%20flight%20time%20from%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20Americans%20often%20see%20Puerto%20Rico%20as%20an%20easy%20tropical%20getaway%20that%20doesn't%20require%20digging%20up%20a%20passport.%20Travelers%20are%20increasingly%20flocking%20to%20the%20island%3A%20Luis%20Mu%C3%B1oz%20Marin%20International%20Airport%2C%20in%20the%20capital%20municipality%20of%20San%20Juan%2C%20received%206.6%20million%20passenger%20arrivals%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20an%208%25%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fdiscover-puerto-rico-celebrates-a-record-breaking-2024-and-looks-ahead-to-2025-growth-302362792.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAir%2520Passenger%2520Growth%253A%2520Luis%2520Mu%25C3%25B1oz%2C2023.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiscover%20Puerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20called%20the%20stat%20%26quot%3Brecord%20growth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Puerto%20Rico%20isn't%20satisfied%20with%20quick%20trips%20anymore.%20They%20want%20you%20to%20stay%20longer%20%E2%80%94%20like%2C%20forever%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20introducing%20favorable%20tax%20incentives%20and%20new%20infrastructure%20to%20make%20your%20everyday%20life%20feel%20like%20a%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224934bae7-90e9-4284-b97c-3debbf55bfb0%5C%22%3ERoom%20for%20a%20rebrand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20mainland%20states%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20fairly%20small.%20Its%20entire%20area%20%E2%80%94%20all%203%2C515%20square%20miles%20%E2%80%94%20could%20fit%20inside%20Connecticut.%20Its%20estimated%20population%2C%20about%203.1%20million%20people%20according%20to%20the%202023%20US%20Census%2C%20is%20roughly%20comparable%20to%20the%20population%20of%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%20and%202023%20combined%2C%2050%2C577%20Americans%20moved%20to%20Puerto%20Rico.%20While%20that's%20not%20a%20particularly%20impressive%20statistic%20%E2%80%94%20the%20island%20only%20captured%20more%20American%20movers%20than%20one%20state%2C%20Wyoming%2C%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20Puerto%20Rico%20has%20plans%20to%20better%20accommodate%20more%20long-term%20residents%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Houses%20in%20Old%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f99aad895d822030323037%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHouses%20in%20Old%20San%20Juan%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3EOscar%20Gutierrez%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20influx%20of%20Americans%20will%20require%20updated%20infrastructure%20to%20make%20them%20happy.%20Though%20cities%20on%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20island%2C%20like%20Condado%2C%20Old%20San%20Juan%2C%20and%20Dorado%2C%20have%20a%20healthy%20number%20of%20Americans%20living%20in%20them%20and%20are%20generally%20better%20equipped%20with%20things%20like%20generators%20and%20cisterns%2C%20other%20parts%20of%20Puerto%20Rico%20are%20still%20lacking.%20In%202019%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfrastructurereportcard.org%2Fstate-item%2Fpuerto-rico%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20American%20Society%20of%20Civil%20Engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ASCE)%20gave%20Puerto%20Rico%20a%20%26quot%3BD-%26quot%3B%20grade%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20citing%20issues%20like%20poor%20roadway%20conditions%20and%20inadequate%20energy%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kreher%2C%20who%20lives%20with%20her%20family%20in%20a%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Condado%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20major%20problem.%20She%20chose%20their%20building%20not%20just%20for%20its%20location%20directly%20on%20the%20ocean%2C%20but%20because%20it%20has%20a%20backup%20generator%2C%20a%20non-negotiable%20for%20her%20setup%20as%20a%20remote%20worker%20who%20requires%20a%20reliable%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Krehers%20haven't%20been%20entirely%20immune%20to%20Puerto%20Rico's%20infrastructure%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20time%20we%20were%20at%20church%2C%20the%20power%20went%20out%20halfway%20through%20the%20sermon%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20have%20a%20generator%2C%26quot%3B%20Kreher%20said.%20But%20when%20these%20things%20happen%2C%20everyone%20takes%20it%20in%20stride%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20wouldn't%20believe%20how%20frequently%20the%20stoplights%20go%20out%20and%20how%20we%20all%20just%20know%20how%20to%20handle%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20a%20villa%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6892065185e81483682f4981%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20a%20villa%20at%20Moncayo.%3Cp%3EThe%20Boundary%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%20passed%20the%20Puerto%20Rico%20Energy%20Public%20Policy%20Act%2C%20which%20set%20a%20goal%20to%20reach%20100%25%20of%20the%20island's%20electricity%20needs%20with%20renewable%20energy%20by%202050.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20Congress%20approved%20%241%20billion%20to%20upgrade%20the%20resilience%20of%20Puerto%20Rico's%20electric%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20enough%20of%20an%20issue%20that%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20trying%20to%20change%20the%20narrative%20and%20expand%20comfortable%20living%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20island.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moncayo.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoncayo%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20resort-style%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-moving-to-neighborhoods-with-golf-yoga-live-like-retirees-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eluxury%20development%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20scheduled%20to%20open%20in%202027%20on%20Puerto%20Rico's%20eastern%20shoreline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarter%20Redd%2C%20the%20developer%20and%20president%20of%20Moncayo%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20development%20was%20designed%20intentionally%20with%20a%20primary%20residential%20community%20%E2%80%94%20not%20vacationers%20%E2%80%94%20in%20mind.%20The%20amenities%20you'd%20expect%20to%20see%20at%20a%20tropical%20residence%20like%20golf%2C%20pickleball%2C%20and%20a%20wellness%20facility%20are%20all%20still%20there%2C%20but%20Moncayo%20is%20also%20enticing%20full-time%20residents%20with%20a%20farm%2C%20a%20PPK-12%20international%20school%2C%20and%20a%20medical%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20more%20and%20more%20people%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20not%20as%20a%20weekend%20getaway%20or%20as%20a%20second%20or%20third%20home%2C%20but%20as%20a%20primary%20home%20community%20and%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20Redd%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20a%20pool%2C%20palm%20trees%2C%20and%20the%20ocean%20from%20a%20balcony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68951fbc194a2d49b8ae3910%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20a%20Moncayo%20balcony%20in%20a%20rendering.%3Cp%3EBoundary%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMoncayo%20isn't%20the%20only%20luxury%20development%20coming%20to%20the%20island.%20Four%20Seasons%20Resort%20and%20Residences%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20set%20to%20open%20in%20late%202025%20just%20thirty%20minutes%20from%20Luis%20Mu%C3%B1oz%20Marin%20International%20Airport%2C%20and%20the%20Mandarin%20Oriental%20Esencia%2C%20a%20residential%20project%20on%202%2C000%20acres%20of%20the%20island's%20southwestern%20coast%2C%20is%20scheduled%20to%20open%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226593b5c2-d81d-41ad-9189-67be16237111%5C%22%3ETaxes%20that%20aren't%20taxing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-living-in-mexico-not-moving-back-pros-cons-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20important%20factor%20in%20leaving%20the%20US.%20Though%20Puerto%20Rico%20isn't%20necessarily%20any%20cheaper%20than%20the%20mainland%2C%20there%20are%20some%20incentives%20that%20can%20sweeten%20the%20deal%20for%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20McCready%2C%20a%2056-year-old%20lawyer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-puerto-rico-from-us-rent-more-expensive-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20San%20Juan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%20He%20pays%20more%20for%20rent%20in%20San%20Juan%20than%20he%20did%20in%20Chicago%2C%20but%20his%20take-home%20pay%20is%20a%20lot%20larger%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-rico-act-60-tax-breaks-capital-gains-bonafide-resident-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAct%2060%2C%20a%20tax%20incentive%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20in%20place%20in%202020%20to%20lure%20Americans%20and%20foreigners%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20in%20hopes%20of%20boosting%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAct%2060%20gives%20residents%20a%204%25%20income%20tax%20rate%2C%20a%2075%25%20discount%20on%20property%20tax%2C%20and%20a%20100%25%20exemption%20from%20capital%20gains%20accrued%20while%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlos%20Fontan%2C%20the%20former%20director%20at%20the%20Office%20of%20Incentives%20for%20Businesses%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20said%20Act%2060%20is%20not%20dissimilar%20to%20the%20ways%20different%20states%20play%20with%20tax%20provisions%20to%20attract%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20of%20a%20man%20on%20a%20beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687695223d5881a51c1d5e89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20McCready%20loves%20the%20beach%20lifestyle%20of%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michael%20McCready%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20people%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20who%20can%20invest%20in%20different%20sectors%20of%20the%20island%2C%20create%20jobs%2C%20and%20create%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Fontan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20our%20socioeconomic%20framework%20on%20the%20island.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFontan%20and%20Humberto%20Mercader%2C%20former%20deputy%20secretary%20of%20the%20Puerto%20Rico%20Department%20of%20Economic%20Development%20and%20Commerce%2C%20believe%20Act%2060%20will%20help%20change%20misconceptions%20about%20Puerto%20Rico%20as%20a%20vacation-only%20destination.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foversightboard.pr.gov%2Fthe-foundation-for-puerto-ricos-economy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Foundation%