administration%20has%20prioritized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-white-house-policy-bitcoin-btc-genius-act-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecrypto-friendly%20policies%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20may%20help%20spur%20crypto%20adoption.%20This%20has%20sparked%20significant%20momentum%20for%20crypto%20markets%2C%20with%20bitcoin%20leading%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-private-equity-retirement-plan-risk-401k-retail-investor-warning-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20opening%20up%20401(k)s%20to%20alternative%20assets%20originally%20raised%20red%20flags%20for%20many%20people%20in%20the%20asset%20management%20and%20financial%20advisory%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20view%2C%20this%20policy%20change%20could%20compromise%20the%20low-risk%2C%20uncomplicated%20nature%20of%20401(k)s%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20part%20of%20why%20many%20people%20trust%20them.%20However%2C%20the%20new%20executive%20order%20could%20mean%20both%20higher%20risk%20and%20reward%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20explore%20this%20new%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Marcus%20Sturdivant%20Sr.%2C%20managing%20member%20of%20The%20ABC%20Squared%20said%2C%20financial%20advisors%20had%20been%20discussing%20these%20issues%20with%20clients%20long%20before%20Trump's%20executive%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac8b3fc8-6b94-4b86-9404-acdae161d138%5C%22%3EPrivate%20equity%20in%20a%20401(k)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20outside%20the%20financial%20sector%20may%20not%20fully%20understand%20what%20private%20equity%20is.%20This%20is%20partially%20because%20the%20private%20equity%20process%20of%20gaining%20exposure%20to%20companies%20that%20are%20not%20publicly%20traded%20has%20been%20reserved%20for%20high-net-worth%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrivate%20equity%20lacks%20the%20transparency%20of%20publicly%20traded%20companies%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20placed%20inside%20a%20fund%2C%20the%20already%20lagging%20effect%20of%20the%20reported%20data%20will%20be%20increased%2C%26quot%3B%20Sturdivant%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20private%20equity%20industry%20also%20funds%20many%20companies%20that%20do%20not%20end%20up%20going%20public%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20lose%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20That%20said%2C%20Sturdivant%20also%20acknowledged%20that%20some%20consider%20private%20equity%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20long-term%20measures%20to%20grow%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20still%20tradeoffs%2C%20and%20opening%20up%20a%20401(k)%20to%20private%20equity%20may%20disadvantage%20some%20users%20due%20to%20timing%2C%20specifically%20the%20lock-up%20period%20on%20an%20investment%2C%20which%20can%20be%20either%20a%20pro%20or%20con.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20older%20and%20near%20retirement%20or%20leave%20it%20as%20an%20inherited%20account%2C%20the%20private%20credit%20portion%20may%20be%20locked%20in%20for%20a%20period%20that%20makes%20the%20ten-year%20period%20to%20use%20an%20inherited%20retirement%20account%20impossible%20to%20access%20the%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b85d453e-5eac-4ab1-8343-bcb6281ade05%5C%22%3ECrypto%20in%20your%20401(k)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20well%20known%20that%20crypto%20is%20subject%20to%20volatility%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20concern%20among%20some%20policymakers%20who%20see%20it%20as%20high-risk%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20Senators%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenate-democrats-probe-crypto-mortgage-plan-risk-fhfa-fannie-freddie-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecently%20raised%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Federal%20Housing%20Finance%20Agency%20(FHFA)%20director%20William%20Pulte%2C%20highlighting%20concerns%20with%