3%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20see%20what%20happened%20between%20when%20something%20was%20handed%20over%20and%20when%20it%20was%20finally%20recycled.%20There%20was%20no%20organised%20system%2C%20just%20a%20mix%20of%20random%20decisions%20and%20hurried%20last-minute%20actions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20spend%20my%20weekends%20interviewing%20shopkeepers%20and%20recyclers%2C%20dissecting%20the%20role%20of%20local%20kabadiwallas%2C%20and%20extracting%20insights%20from%20market%20dynamics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnuj%20noticed%20overwhelming%20issues%3A%20limited%20vendor%20competition%2C%20archaic%20processes%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20transparency%20in%20operations.%20The%20problem%20was%20evident%20%E2%80%94%20a%20scrap%20disposal%20system%20needed%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20Anuj%20would%20discuss%20the%20issue%20with%20his%20colleagues%20and%20friends%2C%20Udaibhan%20Singh%20and%20Amit%20Gautam.%20Once%2C%20over%20dinner%20at%20a%20cosy%20restaurant%2C%20Amit%20proposed%20that%20they%20should%20seize%20this%20opportunity%20and%20start%20a%20business%20together%2C%20incorporating%20technology%20to%20bring%20meaningful%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20moment%2C%20%E2%80%98Let%E2%80%99s%20Scrap%E2%80%99%20was%20born%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20bold%20vision%20to%20create%20a%20roadmap%20for%20responsible%20waste%20disposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20trash%20to%20treasure%20in%20corporates%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20his%20solution%2C%20Anuj%20worked%20on%20a%20systematic%20plan%20to%20dispose%20of%20scrap%20that%20bridged%20the%20gap%20between%20corporate%20structure%20and%20environmental%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FLets-scrap